    • connectMaps

      static void connectMaps​(GameMap m1, GameMap m2, char by)
      Connect the maps by either their x-axes or y-axes. Actors can traverse through the connected maps as if they are the same map, except when Player is on one map, the other will not be displayed.
      Parameters:
      m1 - Map 1 (if connected by x-axes, it will be at North, otherwise at West)
      m2 - Map 2
      by - The axis to connect the maps by
